      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. It exhibits consistent mechanical integrity and a refined aesthetic, reflecting a history of diligent care. Fully inspected and road-ready, this model offers a balanced synthesis of performance and value, ensuring a sophisticated driving experience.",
      "price": 36500.0,
